ointly with a U.S. Treasury yield simulation in a way that reflects the correlation among the 12 factors driving yields in each country. For more on the companion U.S. Treasury simulation, please</em></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/457996383/image_457996383.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743069-weekly-bund-yield-and-euro-forecast-december-6-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 21:00:21"}, {"id": "4743068", "title": "Compass Therapeutics: Near-Term Readout, But Beware The High Stakes In Biliary Cancer", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303781746/image_1303781746.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Thoughtful young man standing with legs crossed\" data-id=\"1303781746\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303781746/image_1303781746.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303781746/image_1303781746.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303781746/image_1303781746.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303781746/image_1303781746.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303781746/image_1303781746.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303781746/image_1303781746.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303781746/image_1303781746.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303781746/image_1303781746.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Klaus Vedfelt</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Topline Summary and Update</h2> <p>When I covered Compass Therapeutics (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CMPX\" title=\"Compass Therapeutics, Inc.\">CMPX</a></span>) <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4700080-compass-therapeutics-stock-interesting-speculative-buy\">back in June</a>, I expressed optimism about their financial situation and the state of their clinical programs. In particular, their anti-angiogenic bispecific antibody had game-changing potential in</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303781746/image_1303781746.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743068-compass-therapeutics-near-term-readout-beware-high-stakes", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 20:54:36"}, {"id": "4743067", "title": "Lululemon Athletica Q3: Demise Of The Company's Growth Greatly Exaggerated", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1388714905/image_1388714905.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Young woman in sports outfit running up the stairs on the city waterfront\" data-id=\"1388714905\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1388714905/image_1388714905.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1388714905/image_1388714905.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1388714905/image_1388714905.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1388714905/image_1388714905.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1388714905/image_1388714905.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1388714905/image_1388714905.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1388714905/image_1388714905.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1388714905/image_1388714905.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">zoranm</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Investment Thesis</strong></h2> <p>The last time <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4682071-lululemon-athletica-stock-q4-earnings-incessant-selling-unwarranted-maintain-buy\">I wrote about</a> <strong>Lululemon Athletica Inc.</strong> (NASDAQ: <span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LULU\" title=\"Lululemon Athletica Inc.\">LULU</a></span>), back in June 2024, I discussed the company\u2019s first quarter performance and argued why there is still value to be gained for long-term investors. I had</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1388714905/image_1388714905.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743067-lululemon-athletica-q3-demise-of-company-growth-greatly-exaggerated", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 20:46:23"}, {"id": "4743063", "title": "PepsiCo: How Beta Can Lead To Alpha", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1172766108/image_1172766108.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Pepsi Beverages Company Signage. Pepsi and PepsiCo is one of the largest beverage producers in the world IV\" data-id=\"1172766108\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"http