der\"></div> <h2>Investment thesis</h2> <p>BK Technologies (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BKTI\" title=\"BK Technologies Corporation\">BKTI</a></span>) is a company that has had an extraordinary 2024 with a performance of 170% YTD; however, the growth prospects are just beginning because of its new line of BKR-9000 radios being rolled</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157428923/image_157428923.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743060-bk-technologies-stock-aggressive-margin-expansion-not-yet-fully-reflected", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 20:21:39"}, {"id": "4743059", "title": "Taylor Morrison Home Corporation Stock Is Still On Sale", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027568389/image_2027568389.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A grey and white modern farmhouse.\" data-id=\"2027568389\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027568389/image_2027568389.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027568389/image_2027568389.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027568389/image_2027568389.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027568389/image_2027568389.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027568389/image_2027568389.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027568389/image_2027568389.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027568389/image_2027568389.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027568389/image_2027568389.jpg?io=getty-c-w24